== Overview ==\nThe following is an enumeration of properties from [[dcmitypes]] vocabulary of [[DC|Dublin Core]] schema. [[dcmitypes]] vocabulary has only objects.\n\n== Prefix ==\ndcmitypes : http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/\n\n== Objects and Properties ==\n* '''<span id='Collection'>Collection</span>''' - as alternative for [[WebEx#scope|WebEx:scope]] or [[Knowledge Tree#Node|Knowledge Tree:Node]] when being a folder\n* '''<span id='Dataset'>Dataset</span>'''\n* '''<span id='Event'>Event</span>''' - [[CUMULATE#User Action|CUMULATE:User Action]]\n* '''<span id='Image'>Image</span>'''\n* '''<span id='InteractiveResource'>InteractiveResource</span>''' - any learning object, [[CUMULATE#User Action.Learning Object|CUMULATE:User Action.Learning Object]], [[CUMULATE#User Progress Assertion.Learning Object|CUMULATE:User Progress Assertion.Learning Object]]\n* '''<span id='MovingImage'>MovingImage</span>'''\n* '''<span id='PhysicalObject'>PhysicalObject</span>'''\n* '''<span id='Service'>Service</span>''' - personalization service, [[CUMULATE#User Action.Application|CUMULATE:User Action.Application]]\n* '''<span id='Software'>Software</span>'''\n* '''<span id='Sound'>Sound</span>'''\n* '''<span id='StillImage'>StillImage</span>'''\n* '''<span id='Text'>Text</span>'''
